{"title":"握手","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自和平国家的朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请听我唱一曲欢迎歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是今天才相见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我们就相识。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能称你是客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我们老朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不仅称你老朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是伟大的和平使者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能说你来自外国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是从我们心上走来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天今天和将来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走的是一条路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一条路上：人类相通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平相通，友谊相通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分国界，不分种族；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林毛泽东的红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高照着我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人民共和国的门口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手！握手！再握手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手，再握手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既不是金钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不是酒和肉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的友谊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争走一条路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这一条路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你赠送我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的花果。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这一条路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们赠送你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是革命花果。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的民主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来互助；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天更会是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分你和我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手，再握手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的朋友。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手，再握手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同走一条路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手，再握手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让全世界的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看伟大的战友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手，并肩高歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九四九年九月六日写）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}